  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a  filmmaker and you recently purchased a box of VHS tapes at a flea market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you need to look through them and select tapes on which occur supernatural, violent, inexplicable scenes, in general everything that can interest the viewer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501370/extras/fd21ec2db1b11a6c4f0aef619f415fb2.poster.avif?t=1743876329\" width=560 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501370/extras/fd21ec2db1b11a6c4f0aef619f415fb2.webm?t=1743876329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501370/extras/fd21ec2db1b11a6c4f0aef619f415fb2.mp4?t=1743876329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple intuitive gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creepy atmosphere in the best traditions of such movies as Skinamarink, V/H/S and others.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short horror packed experience. Play Time 30-60 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You watch different tapes and decide which ones to keep for your movie, if you choose tapes on which nothing happens, you will lose, but you also need to not overlook interesting tapes with mystical, violent or other kind of interesting scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a  filmmaker and you recently purchased a box of VHS tapes at a flea market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you need to look through them and select tapes on which occur supernatural, violent, inexplicable scenes, in general everything that can interest the viewer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501370/extras/fd21ec2db1b11a6c4f0aef619f415fb2.poster.avif?t=1743876329\" width=560 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501370/extras/fd21ec2db1b11a6c4f0aef619f415fb2.webm?t=1743876329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501370/extras/fd21ec2db1b11a6c4f0aef619f415fb2.mp4?t=1743876329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple intuitive gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creepy atmosphere in the best traditions of such movies as Skinamarink, V/H/S and others.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short horror packed experience. Play Time 30-60 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You watch different tapes and decide which ones to keep for your movie, if you choose tapes on which nothing happens, you will lose, but you also need to not overlook interesting tapes with mystical, violent or other kind of interesting scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
